des:
This skill is a short League of Legends Fan-Made Trivia game.
You will be asked 5 random questions, Alexa will list off the possible answers with a corresponding number.
Respond with the number you believe to be correct.
Alexa will keep you updated on your current score between questions and tell you your final results at the end.

This game is not sponsored or endorsed by Riot Games, Inc.
Unofficial trivia game made by a fan
